#* {{quote-journal|en|date=Nov 5, 2017| work=SB Nation |title=Miami players waited to surprise Mark Richt with a Gatorade bath for when they got into the locker room|volume= |number= |author=Harry Lyles Jr. |passage=After Richt got his shower, the Miami players surrounding him while yelling “'''YEET'''!” in unison.}}
#* {{quote-journal|en|date=Oct 11, 2017| work=U.S. News & World Report |title=The Power of an IRL Community: Creating Space for Teens to Unplug and Engage|volume= |number= |author=Caroline Fenkel|passage=Often, my teenagers would exclaim "'''Yeet'''." I am still not quite sure what it means, but I knew they liked to say it, and it was usually after something positive.}}
